{"tid":1403731,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"覺得好灰心嘅人入嚟睇一睇呢條片","createTime":"2019-08-03T21:24:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-03T21:29:47.000Z","uid":85701,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"509a491d103eaac4a0c8740b6b813133b85e5a23","tid":1403731,"uid":85701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T21:24:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/OBQ7YAGRy9Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FOBQ7YAGRy9Y&d=DPPAsuUI5qXcFl7kT6ByvGvf1q1qK4rBaJpe4ZKN2Es%3D&h=612044ad\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/OBQ7YAGRy9Y</a><br />\n<br />\n大家由2：05睇到4：40<br />\n-------------------------------------------------<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">「雖然人類很脆弱，但是正正因為如此才會慢慢變強。」<br />\n「旁觀者也許會覺得這是徒勞無功，但我們的經歷卻不斷累積。」</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6FymeFO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6FymeFO.jpg&h=539af00e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NVqDgSe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNVqDgSe.jpg&h=4f629596&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jwsY1iu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjwsY1iu.jpg&h=0fb56a1e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/chy1Y4V.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fchy1Y4V.jpg&h=0460febd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n-------------------------------------------------<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><br />\n「下級的人要守護更下級的人，過這是作為渺小的人類仍能做到的事。」</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Wm6SmkC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWm6SmkC.jpg&h=19d212d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3HbbBTQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3HbbBTQ.jpg&h=852b7ea0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n-------------------------------------------------<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">「我不要再見到有人死，我要保護大家！」</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/v594WWY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fv594WWY.jpg&h=4be47f7f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6SDELQj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6SDELQj.jpg&h=8614d72f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UW6yQg0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUW6yQg0.jpg&h=178d8df5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n-------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n所以當大家不能相信自己能夠做到時，請你記住和你於香港一起經歷過風雨的各位。總有一天，我們能除下口罩和大家相擁。"},{"pid":"e8fa6cfe5feb118dec3cf05f06f28f4a466d6548","tid":1403731,"uid":85701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T21:25:28.000Z","msg":"光復香港<br />\n時代革命"},{"pid":"5c303df96f406796dbf69596ccf9a2325187f306","tid":1403731,"uid":85701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T21:25:49.000Z","msg":"一定會做到，一定"},{"pid":"30927ffb82b0222716a1d62b7beb2191c8ff5080","tid":1403731,"uid":85701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T21:26:02.000Z","msg":"相信自己"},{"pid":"0faf995cafd1e356f2d539fef8b676ec5410bbbb","tid":1403731,"uid":85701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T21:27:00.000Z","msg":"多謝鋼煉"},{"pid":"bca9930b3e1889804504e8eeb20bb5646a4837d6","tid":1403731,"uid":85701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T21:28:04.000Z","msg":"多謝大家陪左我咁耐"},{"pid":"b8c8916328fadd51a0a66751463bb619f87bb140","tid":1403731,"uid":85701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T21:28:16.000Z","msg":"會做到 一定會"},{"pid":"3ec088842dab42b8052c24333374f62d3ab08419","tid":1403731,"uid":85701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,